{"tid":1873040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】BBC記者想搵經歷過沙士嘅醫護人員","createTime":"2020-02-10T11:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T18:04:48.000Z","uid":86485,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44b1839a3153580a9be1d65631655a0346bc0a4e","tid":1873040,"uid":86485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"#訪問邀請 #interview<br />\n外地傳媒訪問邀請<br />\n<br />\n訪問內容︰<br />\nBBC World News Service想邀請一位曾經歷03年沙士的病人或參與過03年抗疫工作的醫護，主要想討論及對比武漢肺炎與03年沙士的抗疫情況及個人感受。<br />\n<br />\n 負責記者: <br />\nNick Beake (BBC World News Service)<br />\n <a href=\"https://twitter.com/beaking_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbeaking_news&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=37882d5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/beaking_news</a> <br />\n受訪對象身分要求：曾經歷03年沙士的病人或參與過03年抗疫工作的醫護<br />\n形式：Video訪問<br />\n語言：英語或廣東話（有翻譯）<br />\n時間：約45分鐘<br />\n<br />\n如可以幫手，麻煩Telegram聯絡：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/boboboyboy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fboboboyboy&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=299dac71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/boboboyboy</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f678d4b137b9f1ee05a0d6fe52066bd74a27c5c3","tid":1873040,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇日劇鐵手怪傑，先知道BSL4係4級生物安全實驗室，世衛最高級別，劇中話日本2025年先有，但武漢正正就有一間，距離聲稱病毒源頭的巿場只是30公里，有人話有可能係病毒洩漏。"},{"pid":"73e9b3398cbe0252002f32a410ff0d6d05582172","tid":1873040,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"1233032166c572051323629c248ef52b57c22986","tid":1873040,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3eba0bcea244c904